  <body>
    <Header />
	<div style="display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; gap: 1rem;">
	  <div>
	    <h1 style="margin-bottom: 0;">Ronel Xavier</h1>
	    <h2 style="margin-top: 0; color: #8a9fbf;">[ronxvier]</h2>
	  </div>
	  <img
	    src="https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/188875524?v=4"
	    alt="GitHub profile picture"
	    style="width: 80px; height: 80px; border-radius: 50%; object-fit: cover;"
	  />
	</div>

	<p>Currently either Programming, Studying, Weightlifting, Writing, Climbing, Wrestling, Reading, or Running.</p>
	<p>This site exists primarily to document the <a href="../projects">[projects]</a> I've completed as I add more throughout uni. I've also added a blog section, which I may use to keep record of my notes, given the blog entries use the same markdown format as <a href="https://obsidian.md" target = "_blank">[obsidian.md]</a>.</p>
    <Footer />

  </body>
</html>



